Age vs size plot
```{r}
ggplot(DendroMerge, aes(x = PithHand, y = `Diameter (CM)`, color= ID2)) +
  labs( x= "Pith Year", y = "Diameter (cm)", title = "Diameter vs Pith Date") +
  geom_point(shape=18, size= 3)+
  geom_smooth( method = "lm", se = FALSE, size = 1.5)+
  scale_y_continuous(
    limits = c(0,100)
  ) +
scale_x_continuous(
  limits = c(1985,2020)
)+ theme_minimal()
```


